{"data":{"post":{"id":"d3d08a6a-6819-5246-a7b6-4711aa297d19","html":"<p>  呼吸，看似非常自然的一种现象，为何在瑜伽中如此重要呢？</p>\n<p>个人理解：通过呼吸，可以唤醒对内在自我的觉知。</p>\n<p>除了我们熟悉的自然呼吸，还有腹式呼吸或称隔膜呼吸、肋间呼吸或称胸式呼吸、锁骨呼吸或称肩式呼吸、完全式呼吸，见下图。</p>\n<p>  瑜伽体式配合呼吸，可参考以下原则：</p>\n<p>  起为吸，落为呼；</p>\n<p>  开为吸，合为呼；</p>\n<p>  前屈为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  后弯为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  体转为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  侧弯为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  挤压为呼，还原为吸。</p>\n<p><figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/9b0b4/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 33.65500603136309%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2         \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/48538/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/bed0f/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png 200w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/5fd34/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png 400w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/48538/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png 800w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/9b0b4/2-瑜伽中的呼吸方式.png 829w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">breathing in yoga</figcaption></figure></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2019-02-04/yoga-knowledge/","prefix":"2019-02-04"},"frontmatter":{"title":"(2) Breathing in yoga","author":"文:Jane","category":"yoga","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/stati